# Example Ollama Modelfile for GPU-optimised inference on Jetson TX2.
#
# Key parameters:
#   num_ctx  – context window in tokens. The default (32 768) allocates a
#              ~1.8 GB KV cache that, combined with the model weights, exceeds
#              the TX2's 8 GB of unified memory and triggers the OOM killer.
#              2048 keeps the KV cache at ~112 MB.
#   num_gpu  – number of transformer layers to offload to the GPU.
#              Set to 99 for a model that fits entirely on GPU (e.g. 3 B),
#              or to 20 for qwen2.5:7b (partial offload).

FROM qwen2.5:3b
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
PARAMETER num_gpu 99
